    <h2 class="sect-title">About Spruce Cliff</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The neighborhood is bound by 37 Street W on the west, Shaganappi Golf Course to the east, Bow Trail on the South and the CPR Tracks on the North.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Spruce Cliff homes for sale include an eclectic mix of apartments, condos, and townhomes with two major development projects namely the Westgate Park high-rise residential tower and the Sandalwood Developmentsâ€™ Copperwood condo complex coming up in the neighborhood soon.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Despite the popularity of the Spruce Cliff real estate, home prices are quite affordable with single detached as well as condo units available.</p>
